channel.title: Bloodless - Young Saver [Electronic Pop]
channel.description:
Long story short, I'm a drummer by trade but haven't written songs in ages. Auxy has given me the freedom and versatility to write on the move and I've actually managed to cobble 12 songs together this year. Album coming shortly, this is the first song I've released. Thank you Auxy for making me create again!
https://soundcloud.com/youngsaver/bloodless
